                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="3">
                            <para>Pigtail Connector to Ground B-</para>
                            <para>High resistance could indicate an open circuit in the UVC (under the valve cover)
                                harness or in the glow plug.
                            </para>
                            <para>Glow plug resistance should measure .1 to 6 ohms dependent upon engine temperature.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
